# Name Capitalization Formatting 

## Project Overview
This project demonstrates how to standardize the capitalization of names stored in a database using SQL's `INITCAP()` function.  
It converts names with mixed or inconsistent cases into proper case format, enhancing data consistency.

## Dataset

### Names Table

| Column Name | Data Type    | Description          |
|-------------|--------------|----------------------|
| Name        | VARCHAR(100) | Name of the person (mixed case) |

## SQL Queries

###  Create Names Table and Insert Sample Data
```sql
CREATE TABLE "Names" ("Name" VARCHAR(100));

INSERT INTO "Names" ("Name") VALUES
('rAVI kUMAR'),
('priya sharma'),
('amit PATEL'),
('NEHA gupta');
